.page#contacts(ng-controller="ContactsController")
  .arrow.up.dark.no_margin_bottom(ng-click="scrollToElement('header')")
  
  h2.title Contattaci

  .page_content.no_margin_top.no_margin_bottom
    .contacts
      form.contacts_form#message-form(name="contact_form" ng-submit="sendEmail($event)")
        .form_group
          label(for='full-name') Nome e Cognome*
          input#full-name(type='text' placeholder='Nome e Cognome' required='' ng-model="contact_form_data.full_name" ng-disabled="contact_form_data.send_success || is_sending")
        .form_group
          label(for='email-field') Email*
          input#email-field(type='email' placeholder='Email' required='' ng-model="contact_form_data.email" ng-disabled="contact_form_data.send_success || is_sending")
        .form_group
          label(for='message-field') Messaggio
          textarea#message-field(rows='5' placeholder="Il tuo messaggio" ng-model="contact_form_data.message" ng-disabled="contact_form_data.send_success || is_sending")
        .form_group
          label.fake
          .notice(ng-show="contact_form.$submitted")
            p.success(ng-show="contact_form_data.send_success")
              | Messaggio inviato con successo. Grazie per aver scelto Alberti Business, sarai contattato al pi√π presto.
            p.error(ng-show="!contact_form_data.full_name || !contact_form_data.email || !contact_form_data.message")
              | Impossibile inviare il messaggio, per favore controlla di aver inserito correttamente tutti i dati richiesti.
        .form_group
          button.button.blue(type="submit" ng-class="{'sending': is_sending, 'success': contact_form_data.send_success}" ng-disabled="contact_form_data.send_success || is_sending")
            span(ng-show="!contact_form_data.send_success") Invia
            span(ng-show="contact_form_data.send_success") Messaggio Inviato!


  .arrow.down.dark.no_margin_top(ng-click="scrollToElement('partners')")

